OL,8,GThe thrilling true story of the Apollo
OL,9,Gmission that very nearly never made it
OL,10,Ghome. Tom Hanks excels as Jim Lovell,
OL,11,Gtrapped thousands of miles away in a
OL,12,Gbarely-working spaceship. Ron Howard
OL,13,Gbuilds the tension to fever-point,
OL,14,Geven though we know the outcome. We
OL,15,Gare proud to present this movie on an
OL,16,Goriginal 35mm print.
